Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:23:03.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,夕暮れ落ちる前に白い月が昇る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:23:03.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,,夜幕還未完全降臨 潔白的月光便灑落大地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:09.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,春風優しく2つの影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:09.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,春風溫柔地拂過二人的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:16.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,ささやくように包んでいたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:16.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,靜悄悄地圍繞在你我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:29.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,初めてこんなに誰かを想った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:29.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,第一次發現在腦海中 有著一個身影揮之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:35.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,いつもどうしていいのかわからなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:35.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,總是一直不知道該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:42.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,君への想いはこぼれるほどあるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:42.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,,明明對你的思念早已溢滿心田
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.03,0:23:49.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,つないだ右手もぎこちないキスも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.03,0:23:49.49,EDCN,,0,0,0,,緊緊握住的右手也好 笨拙生疏的接吻也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.49,0:23:56.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,それだけがこの世界の全てだった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.49,0:23:56.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,僅僅只是這些 卻已然成為了我世界的一切的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.07,0:24:02.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,今日も君からもらった言葉を抱きしめている
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.07,0:24:02.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,今天又一次將你的言語擁入心中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.92,0:24:09.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,私にとってそれはまるで月明かり
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.92,0:24:09.01,EDCN,,0,0,0,,因那對於我而言宛若月明之光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:19.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,二人で見上げたあの時みたいにきれい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:19.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,正如我們那天一起仰望的 那般美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:58.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,なんとなく頭の中で君が  離れなくなっていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:58.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,不知為何  你的身影一直縈繞在我的腦海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:19.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,途切れの会話だね いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:19.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我們倆的對話總是斷斷續續呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:27.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,息も吐き出せないほどのことを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:27.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,和你交談時  我總覺得呼吸困難
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:30.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,目が合った瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:30.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,在眼神交會的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:40.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,また何かが胸を貫いてゆく  今!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:40.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我感覺彷彿有什麼擊中了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:47.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,大好きな人がイマココに居る、居るんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:47.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,現在我最喜歡的人就在我眼前  在我眼前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:54.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,最高の毎日は恋の晴れパレーパレード
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:54.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,每天都幸福得像戀愛大遊行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:03:01.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,近づきたい 誰よりも君に今、いま以上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:03:01.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我想靠近你  我想靠得比誰都近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:11.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,会いたくて会いに行く  笑顔また見つけに行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:11.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我想見你  我現在就去尋找你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,找到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我三班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,二班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,三個人全分開了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有一起的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.96,0:01:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,田徑部一個都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,反正社團活動能見面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,會不會有新生加入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,最好多來點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.95,0:01:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  我都忘了海報
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,比良拜託我弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.71,0:01:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,相當律師那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.47,0:01:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,要幫忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我們也要大展拳腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要全力以赴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.81,0:01:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,對不  茜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,從今天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.11,0:01:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我就要上國三了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,各位同學  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻花盛開的四月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,新的一年將從今天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,希望各位新生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,能夠珍惜剛入學時的新鮮感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,讓今後的校園生活變充實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,各位國二國三的學生也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,換班之後……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜  冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是國中生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也分地位高低
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,上流和下流
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,華麗的社團和不起眼的社團
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,外貌和成績
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,利用一切武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,試探彼此的等級地位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真有人氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,浪漫  真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,受歡迎的人  真火大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,（聽我說聽我說）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,（怎麼了）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,（一點都不痛）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,（接招）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,（好痛）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,（真的？）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:04:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,（你練過？）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,（沒啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,（毫無感覺）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,（混蛋）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,（好痛）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,（誰叫你這麼有人氣）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是我  心咲  還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,小學三年級時一個班的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你是田徑部的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,涼子來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,都請回座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但願能來一幫新生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也國三了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好  全力以赴囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,犬大大募集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,犬耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-小太  -小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,給我看小說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,才不給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,鑰匙我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,預備  跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,茜  手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,水野  還能更快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-歡迎回來  -歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,說是今天去外面吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要沖澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這就去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子他爸  把電視關了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,兩位客人  有請入座
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1183,970)\frz4.154\fs50}好啊  加油喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就知道玩LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,之前那個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,水來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小太郎不用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝自助飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喝茶就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,多吃點  社團那麼累
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:09:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,沙拉義大利麵和自助飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？就這點？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽  點這個如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,奶油焗菜和義式千層餅也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要我幫你選嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,已經點義大利麵了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,能吃完嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小太郎要點飲料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,小太郎要自助飲料對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子他媽  能按下服務鈴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小太郎  在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,要自助飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,大宰說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,『人生在世
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  真是無比煎熬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,壓得人喘不過氣的大事業』
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,茜姐  要給你點個清炒菠菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,含鐵量高  對身體有好處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,點太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,茜會吃光的  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,大會快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,得多吃點對身體好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,肉呼呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我去拿飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,茜  把大家的也接來  老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸要檸檬蘇打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,茜  拿得下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,同一個班的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我家茜一個班的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,小太郎真是的  什麼都不說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,承蒙您女兒照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是安曇小太郎的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,承蒙您兒子照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  你好你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,請問菜是否上齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼鬼  這麼多  真搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,喔  蠻可愛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子他爸  麻煩你別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小太郎也到青春期了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,小太郎  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好想捏捏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那……那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的事  請不要在學校說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,謝……謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,穿這身就不害羞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那天之後  我們就沒說過話了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然都很在意彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那各組的人員分配就確定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,今天放學之後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,為運動會做準備  有各負責區域的說明會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,等最終練習結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,請參照手上的表
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,根據自己的分組前往對應的教室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,全員似乎都到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:13:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我是田徑部的比良
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,器材組是以田徑部為中心進行工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,希望大家能協助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,去年參與過的人應該清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,工作的大致內容是提前準備好各項目的器材
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,翹起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？LINE？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,去年  班裡負責的人建了一個群
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,超方便的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,茜也去問問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,各位  能來一趟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,沒社團活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,翹了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,今天在家寫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,寫完了給我看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？小太郎真小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,才不小氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,小氣太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,（疼  痛）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz339.8\pos(1025,655)}有男生的LINE嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz339.3\pos(910,829)}我知道藤堂和吉岡的LINE的  放心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1245,615)\frz338.1}多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz339.6\pos(1020,434)}器材組
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,還差翹毛君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz346.5\pos(998,497)}這是保障組的聯絡網
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz346.8\pos(767,825)}4月14日午休時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz346.3\pos(934,952)}請全體器材組在體育倉庫集合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz345.6\pos(651,1037)}請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,吶  永原
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天看LINE了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,都不回話的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  在遊戲廳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,都說抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啦  節子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,居然放女人鴿子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,太鼓打出全combo了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,太鼓？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,太鼓鐵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說永原超厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,超帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:15:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好想看好想看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜  去廁所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,下週有祭典訓練哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz10.73\pos(1403,459)}老師連我內衣繡著玫瑰都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那個短篇小說很有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,太宰用第一人稱獨白的形式寫了女生的心境
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,女生的感受  一般的男生怎麼可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,之前說過的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:20.69,Notes,,0,0,0,,煮麵  happy end
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,煮麵？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,大型民謠搖滾樂團happy end的首張專輯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,成員後來全成了音樂界的大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很厲害的樂團
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,想什麼時候還我都行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這本書要買嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要這本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這本送你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,各式各樣的書都讀讀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,安曇  器材組集會你沒來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,別的人都在工作呢  你也得來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,計分板還在體育倉庫  去拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那……那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我忘記聯繫你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,器材組有通知的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,LINE  能告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,建了個擔任組的群
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在沒帶手機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那就……那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:20:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪我……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可是  你的社團怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在LINE上說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,人多好辦事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,弄髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,背後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,已經可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真的對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:22:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1200,450)\frz343.1}請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.95,0:22:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,大宰說過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,「何謂幸福感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,也許就像沉在河底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,微微發光的金砂吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.07,0:22:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,整死你
